01:38.865 --> 01:43.737 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Donald Trump
campaigned in
the Tar Heel State, where he
went after Hillary

01:43.770 --> 01:47.374 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
