e-mails.

01:49.209 --> 01:55.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: Speaking in secret
to a foreign
bank, Hillary Clinton said her
dream is for

01:55.182 --> 01:57.250 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
