in neighboring
Ohio, in Cleveland.

02:12.566 --> 02:17.871 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON: On
Wednesday night,
Donald Trump did something no
other presidential

02:17.904 --> 02:20.207 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
nominee has ever done.

02:20.240 --> 02:25.245 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
