rivals sat
practically side-by-side, at the
Alfred E.

02:40.694 --> 02:42.729 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Smith Dinner in New York.

02:42.763 --> 02:48.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
