(LAUGHTER)

03:23.837 --> 03:27.607 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON: Now,
actually I did.

03:27.641 --> 03:29.476 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's called preparation.

03:29.509 --> 03:34.614 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
