the U.S. Army
in Iraq.

03:38.218 --> 03:47.027 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KHIZR KHAN, Father of Killed
U.S. Soldier:
I want to ask Mr. Trump, would
my son have

03:47.060 --> 03:48.662 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
