04:06.079 --> 04:12.219 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Ayotte faces a
difficult reelection
bid, and hers is one the tossup
seats that

04:12.252 --> 04:16.189 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
