plant, killing
13 workers, including four
Iranians.

05:31.965 --> 05:36.169 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Explosions and gunfire echoed
throughout that
area for hours.

05:36.203 --> 05:41.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
