the foreign
policy of America."

06:52.712 --> 06:57.350 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In Washington, White House
spokesman Josh
Earnest expressed concern about
the leader's

06:57.384 --> 06:59.219 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
recent pronouncements.

06:59.252 --> 07:01.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSH EARNEST, White House Press
Secretary:
We have seen too many troubling
public statements

07:01.788 --> 07:04.724 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
from President Duterte over the
last several
months.

07:04.758 --> 07:11.798 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
