advance the
interests of either country.

07:15.568 --> 07:19.839 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The U.S. and the
Philippines
have been allies for 70 years.

07:19.873 --> 07:26.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
