from Donald
Trump right now.

11:58.151 --> 12:01.187 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It's just there
are stories
all over the map.

12:01.220 --> 12:03.890 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
