of the ticket.

12:30.383 --> 12:34.454 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But then there was the "Access
Hollywood"
tape, the second debate, and now
we have seen

12:34.487 --> 12:36.823 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
a steep decline in Trump's
numbers.

12:36.856 --> 12:42.028 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the presidential race has
always had an
impact on Senate races, but, as
his hole gets

12:42.061 --> 12:46.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
