number of ticket-splitters
that these Republicans need in
order to survive.

12:46.633 --> 12:52.972 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Lisa, talk
about how then
exactly the Democrats' chances
look for taking

12:53.006 --> 12:54.073 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
