map.

12:55.541 --> 12:56.943 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I love it.

12:56.976 --> 12:59.779 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a case where again
Republicans walked
in with a disadvantage.

12:59.812 --> 13:03.716 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
