Democrats need.

13:24.437 --> 13:29.375 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Then we have got six these
remaining swing
states that, of those, Democrats
need to win

13:29.409 --> 13:31.110 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
three.

13:31.144 --> 13:34.647 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, is that maybe a win in
Pennsylvania and
New Hampshire, where Kelly
Ayotte, who was

13:34.681 --> 13:37.150 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
