having a

13:42.288 --> 13:43.256 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
problem.

13:43.289 --> 13:45.558 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They were outperforming Trump a
month ago.

13:45.591 --> 13:47.260 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
