13:47.293 --> 13:51.831 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And Democrats need to just pick
up three of
this group of six swing Senate
seats.

13:51.864 --> 13:54.367 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, it's getting more and more
within their
reach.

13:54.400 --> 13:58.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, Nathan, if
things look
a little better for the
Democrats in the Senate,

13:58.971 --> 13:59.939 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
