NATHAN GONZALES: Thank you.

15:12.912 --> 15:21.320 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Next: A judge
ruled today that
a Maryland man accused of
stealing massive

15:21.354 --> 15:27.260 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
amounts of information from the
