Agency was a flight risk and
will remain in

15:27.293 --> 15:29.028 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
federal custody.

15:29.061 --> 15:30.830 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
William Brangham has the story.

15:30.863 --> 15:34.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: This past
August, Harold
Martin III was arrested at his
home in the

15:34.767 --> 15:36.903 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Maryland suburbs of Washington,
D.C.

15:36.936 --> 15:42.141 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In his house, investigators
discovered the
equivalent of half-a-billion
pages of documents

15:42.175 --> 15:47.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and electronic data, some
allegedly taken
from the NSA's headquarters at
nearby Fort

15:47.180 --> 15:49.048 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Meade.

15:49.081 --> 15:53.519 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Among the documents were ones
marked top-secret
and also tools used by the NSA
to hack into

15:53.553 --> 15:56.055 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
