sense of humor
is considered flagrantly
un-American.

26:33.158 --> 26:40.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I remember George W. Bush at
that dinner
in 2000 standing up and saying,
look at this

26:40.232 --> 26:46.538 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
