white tie and
tails, the haves and the
have-mores.

26:46.572 --> 26:47.739 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Some people call you the elite.

26:47.773 --> 26:49.441 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I call you my base.

26:49.475 --> 26:52.978 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, he was laughing at himself
that he was
the candidate of the well-off or
whatever

26:53.011 --> 26:53.979 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
else.

26:54.012 --> 26:57.683 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I think Trump just missed
this completely.

26:57.716 --> 27:04.857 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I agree with David that
there was too
much of an edge even in
Clinton's remarks.

27:04.890 --> 27:12.364 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But Trump just missed the whole
thing, and
it was -- it's a tone-deafness
that's -- it's

27:12.397 --> 27:14.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
unsettling.

27:14.199 --> 27:18.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, let's talk
a little bit,
Mark and David, about what
Hillary Clinton

27:18.303 --> 27:20.138 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
is saying out on the trail.

27:20.172 --> 27:25.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She isn't hitting as many
campaign stops as
he is, but, David, we see today
she is talking

27:25.511 --> 27:29.715 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to voters about -- she is saying
things like,
think about the future of the
country.

27:29.748 --> 27:34.520 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What sort of future do you want,
what sort
of country do you want?

27:34.553 --> 27:36.088 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
She said at one point, you live
your life.

27:36.121 --> 27:38.023 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I will do the worrying.

27:38.056 --> 27:40.392 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Does it sound like she's already
winding this
thing down?

27:40.425 --> 27:45.264 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Well, there is a
lot of let's
go for the landslide talk out of
the Democratic

27:45.297 --> 27:49.935 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Party, which a normal -- the
normal rules
of campaigning, that's a no-no.

27:49.968 --> 27:51.236 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You want your people to come
out.

27:51.270 --> 27:53.338 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You don't want them to think,
oh, we got this
one in the bag.

