verb or what
it is.

29:21.793 --> 29:26.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I do think it makes sense for
the Democrats
to -- that Trump has done a
favor for them

29:26.999 --> 29:32.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
as far as turnout, because there
isn't that
kind of enthusiasm and passion
for her candidacy.

29:32.671 --> 29:38.377 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And by his question of
legitimacy, the idea
that your vote does count, that
