29:55.861 --> 29:57.496 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I think, in that sense, it
works.

29:57.529 --> 30:02.501 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I don't think we're going to
get that
-- not going to take us to the
top of the

30:02.534 --> 30:03.502 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
mountain.

30:03.535 --> 30:04.503 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, is he doing
her that favor?

30:04.536 --> 30:05.504 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

30:05.537 --> 30:06.505 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Go ahead.

30:06.538 --> 30:08.173 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Go ahead, David.

30:08.206 --> 30:08.974 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Yes, I would say I
ran into
a guy in Louisiana, in New
Orleans, because

30:09.007 --> 30:11.209 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
