after helping
his siblings with loans.

37:27.078 --> 37:30.048 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So Jordan's parents asked his
grandparents
to co-sign.

37:30.081 --> 37:32.851 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And when his debt piled up, the
loan servicer
came calling.

37:32.884 --> 37:39.057 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MELODI HOEFT, Mother of Jordan
Hoeft: My father
co-signed for some of the kids'
loans after

37:39.090 --> 37:43.795 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
