their state's
top law enforcement officer.

39:19.691 --> 39:22.393 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA MADIGAN, Illinois Attorney
General: I
have seen an increasing number
of fraud complaints

39:22.427 --> 39:24.929 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
from current and former higher
education students.

39:24.963 --> 39:28.099 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LIZZIE O'LEARY: Lisa Madigan is
the attorney
general for Illinois.

39:28.132 --> 39:32.270 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
After noticing a rise in
complaints against
companies involved in higher
education, Madigan

39:32.303 --> 39:35.573 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
filed lawsuits against several
for-profit
schools.

39:35.607 --> 39:39.210 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
