Navient?

39:41.045 --> 39:44.215 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA MADIGAN: It was the volume
of complaints
that we received and the serious
nature of

39:44.249 --> 39:45.984 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
