options.

39:57.662 --> 40:01.432 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LIZZIE O'LEARY: The majority of
student loans
are federal and originate with
the Department

40:01.466 --> 40:06.904 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of Education, but they're
contracted out to
a handful of companies who
manage the payments.

40:06.938 --> 40:13.344 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's a $140 billion industry
