40:15.113 --> 40:17.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA MADIGAN: Most of the time,
what they
do if someone is struggling is,
they will

40:17.782 --> 40:22.120 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
