certainly not
going to make that debt any more
manageable.

40:25.356 --> 40:27.692 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
In fact, it will often tend to
grow that debt.

40:27.725 --> 40:30.328 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LIZZIE O'LEARY: There are
several ways to
reduce monthly payments.

40:30.361 --> 40:35.667 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Deferment or forbearance
temporarily postpones
payments, but interest may
continue to accrue

40:35.700 --> 40:37.869 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
