into income-driven

41:17.442 --> 41:19.277 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
repayment programs.

41:19.310 --> 41:23.948 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have been strong advocates
for streamlining
the enrollment process to make
it easier for

41:23.981 --> 41:25.450 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
borrowers."

41:25.483 --> 41:28.486 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
"PBS NewsHour" requested an
interview with
the Department of Education.

41:28.519 --> 41:30.355 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
