tracking complaints.

41:49.841 --> 41:54.212 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The agency has started
monitoring many key
financial players, including
loan service

41:54.245 --> 41:55.947 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
companies.

41:55.980 --> 41:57.682 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SETH FROTMAN, Consumer Finance
Protection
Bureau: And there's an amazing
government

41:57.715 --> 42:03.221 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
